        "reason": "D3.8 FTTS compliance: added missing context fields (transaction_initiator, data_flow_direction, entity_category, message_id) to match implemented adapter code. Moved event_timestamp to optional (not always present in RabbitMQ messages)."
      }
    ]
  }
}
